{"id": 2440, "genre": 1001, "title": "和人相处初期，对方做了啥会让你好感全无？", "description": "你会一票否决的那个瞬间。（题图来自：istock ©kbeis）", "record_count": 10057, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180627102201KJ2dzCy50LnS7XDu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-06T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 291328, "content": "虚伪，不够真心，藏着坏心", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 291584, "content": "吸烟，吃槟榔", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393252}, {"id": 292352, "content": "不停讲话 声音特别大\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377936}, {"id": 292097, "content": "吃饭不买单", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396554}, {"id": 294145, "content": "阴阳怪气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1410516}, {"id": 291330, "content": "穿丝袜", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392374}, {"id": 291586, "content": "斤斤计较", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581744}, {"id": 291331, "content": "当面一套 背后一套", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250694}, {"id": 291332, "content": "把偷懒当本事 到处宣扬自己怎么偷懒还有就是全身散发负能量 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1250694}, {"id": 291588, "content": "指甲很长。歧视女性，残疾人，胖子等。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096161}, {"id": 291333, "content": "迟到", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938383}, {"id": 291589, "content": "笃定的坚持自己意见，不接受他人其他意见，你若是说了便喋喋不休。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376167}, {"id": 291334, "content": "出去吃饭，一遍一遍的叫服务员，还说这不行那不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392382}, {"id": 291590, "content": "问性生活状态", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 201929}, {"id": 292614, "content": "回复消息不及时，聊着聊着就不回微信了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1400654}, {"id": 291335, "content": "刚相处就热吻", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392384}, {"id": 291591, "content": "公共场合高声说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393244}, {"id": 292103, "content": "尬聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 356317}, {"id": 292872, "content": "刷快手抖音开扬声器。(*Ӧ)σ怼他", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399891}, {"id": 291337, "content": "刷抖音，骂脏话，肩膀一层头皮屑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973417}, {"id": 291338, "content": "全程都在玩手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392390}, {"id": 291594, "content": "没礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761850}, {"id": 291339, "content": "鼻毛外漏、\n口臭、\n大烟牙。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363478}, {"id": 291340, "content": "对不清楚的事物，评价都是垃圾。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371536}, {"id": 291596, "content": "自负", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390086}, {"id": 291341, "content": "提大音量强行插话", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1390953}, {"id": 291597, "content": "贴标签", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075530}, {"id": 292877, "content": "在其他人面前，拿她的优点和我的缺点做比较，还不说别人坏话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403649}, {"id": 291598, "content": "没有礼貌", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393346}, {"id": 291343, "content": "拜托的事转头就忘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392396}, {"id": 291599, "content": "非常有心机想套话的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393350}, {"id": 291344, "content": "打呼噜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392404}, {"id": 296464, "content": "说话不过脑子。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419143}, {"id": 291345, "content": "抱怨这抱怨那 丧得不行", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392414}, {"id": 291346, "content": "给所有答案不同分数，到一定分数的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379658}, {"id": 291602, "content": "气场不搭！", "image": "img/option/option/20180707220529ue38pwYncVz2SCGU", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718332}, {"id": 291347, "content": "密码，人还不能有个缺点啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1239400}, {"id": 291603, "content": "不分场合随性抽烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393360}, {"id": 291348, "content": "张口闭口“我们是兄弟”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296079}, {"id": 291604, "content": "讲话夸张到让人尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207346}, {"id": 292628, "content": "易怒。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1400683}, {"id": 291349, "content": "剧烈的审美差距", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689835}, {"id": 291605, "content": "各种装逼！哪里都有熟人，啥事都能办，和你最铁，就是不差钱！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393371}, {"id": 291350, "content": "给别人起嘲讽意味的外号", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381732}, {"id": 291351, "content": "狂妄自大", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378233}, {"id": 291607, "content": "刚认识没多久就找我帮忙", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393376}, {"id": 291863, "content": "抠鼻屎", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715165}, {"id": 291608, "content": "装模作样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393399}, {"id": 291353, "content": "说哦 额 呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392443}, {"id": 291609, "content": "行为方式和我三观不符", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393405}]}